        "images": [
            {
                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2607.05390/2607.05390v1/x2.png",
                "caption": "Figure 2:Overview of our annotation pipeline.We convert multi-view video and tactile streams into dense annotations for deformable object dynamics.\nWe first reconstruct high-fidelity dynamic geometry using per-frame 3D Gaussian Splatting.\nThen, we perform markerless 2D tracking, lift the tracks into 3D, and optimize for temporal and multi-view consistency and physical plausibility.",
